post_text: North Pointe's first Annual Old School Carnival is tonight from 6-8pm. We will be selling all your favorite carnival food including popcorn, cotton candy, corn dogs, nachos and so much more! Your $2 admission gets you 8 tickets to play our carnival games. And while you are here you can enjoy our annual Powder Puff game. All the proceeds go to North Pointe's wonderful student activities.

post_text: During 8th hour today police closed a portion of 43rd Avenue because of a gas leak in an apartment complex near the school. Since the Prep's parking lot was inaccessible for junior high pick-up, Principal Gow worked with the Glendale Police Department to relocate student pick-up to the Target parking lot.
